GRID SYSTEM

1-add a style tag a the top and add this to see the columns better:

<style>
    .box{
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
    padding: 10px;
    text-align: center
 }

</style>

2-NON REPONSIVE GRID
ALL GRID SHOULD BE WRAP IN THE CLASS OF ROW

12 1 Columns

-create a div with the class of row
-create 2 more divs, 
-one with the  class col s1 and other with the class of box (from the style tag)
-add numbers inside the box class starting with 1 until 12

  <div class="col 1">
   <div class="box">
     1
   </div>
</div>

Do it 12 times all inside a div with class row

3- 3 4 colomns divs

<div class="col s4">
   <div class="box">1</div>
 </div>

4- 2 6 columns div

 <div class="col s6">
    <div class="box">1</div>
 </div>

5- 8 & 4

  <div class="row">
        <div class="col s8">
         <div class="box">1</div>
       </div>
       <div class="col s4">
     <div class="box">2</div>
   </div>
 </div>


